0%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>@KittensForDays we have the official hand off! Our family is calling her Princess Taters as she gets ready to come to her new home outside of Boston! Her foster mama here has been AMAZING! And bestie may visit us in the future when she comes see family nearby. This has been truly a beautiful journey! As promised, I’m gonna keep y’all posted!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/87LByqr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is Princess Taters’ new fancy bed. We got her something special: a little designer woven cat bed from Croatia.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/T0rQYwk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And this is Princess Taters’ new castle. We got her a small cuddle pillow with her new big sister Lucy’s picture printed on it. The real Lucy is in the corner sun bathing in the bedroom. She’s a golden retriever who loves cuddles and cats.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jA0D8N9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[missourigal]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When someone leaves a supportive comment and tosses your post an accolade.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/K9zmKO0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9pOSjA4.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fun stuff.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/K9zmKO0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[deafkitten]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>